---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Support — YOUTUBE PLAYABLES" description="Get help with YOUTUBE PLAYABLES: gameplay questions, controls, and troubleshooting.">
  <a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Support.</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-body">Need a hand? Every game page includes a full guide, player instructions, and an FAQ section. Start with the answers below.</p>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">How do I play a game?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-body">Open any title from the <a href="/playables" class="text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">playables library</a> and follow the on-page "How to play" and "Player instructions" sections.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Do games work on mobile?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-body">Yes. Every game supports mouse, keyboard, and touch, and is laid out responsively for phones, tablets, and desktops.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Are my scores saved?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-body">High scores and recently played games are stored locally in your browser. Clearing site data resets them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Something isn't working.</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-body">Try "New game" to reset the board, and refresh the page. For persistent issues, check that JavaScript is enabled.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/playables" class="mt-10 inline-block text-sm text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">← Back to playables</a>
  </main>
</Layout>
